## Purpose

This file is the concise, always-loaded owner profile. Use it when writing,
reasoning, positioning, or making decisions on the owner's behalf. It is not a
full biography — that lives in the Guide and in the Memory MCP. This is stable,
high-signal context for judgment and voice.

Keep it short. Deep, atomized facts belong in memory (retrieved on demand);
only what should be in front of every turn belongs here.

